amesmarket

Class LoadCaseControl

  • java.lang.Object
    • amesmarket.LoadCaseControl

  • public class LoadCaseControl
extends java.lang.Object
    Model of the LoadCase Control File. Scenarios are referenced by their 'userland' number. Scenario 1 in the file is Scenario 1 in the getters/setters. The design of this class assumes 'file-based' scenarios. It should be relatively easy, but is not implemented, to use other input sources instead of files (e.g. a stream from the somewhere.)
